    "description": "A SUPER REALISTIC (ahem..) alien sniper simulator!<br>Use your super quick reaction skills to outwit the alien blighters and snipe your way to victory!<br>Play through the story or play for high scores, either way, your skills will be put to the test as a SUPER ALIEN SNIPER!<br><br>Help Commander Robot to defeat the alien enemies, with your quick reaction and supreme focus skills. Each round will introduce new conditions for victory.<br>You may have to follow on screen commands and shoot right, or maybe shoot left!<br>You may have to follow voice commands and ignore the on screen prompts!<br>You may even have to ignore Commander Robot all together!<br>The one thing that is without doubt, you'll have to use your extreme focus as a Super Alien Sniper to the max!<br><br><strong>Features</strong>  <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple and intuitive controls via mouse, keyboard, or controller<br></li><li>Story mode and an endless mode to smash your high scores<br></li><li>Fast-paced gameplay that will require excellent brain power and the aforementioned focus!<br></li><li>Bonus: Commander Robot Album, unlocked after finishing story mode!</li></ul>",
